  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First, the couple, the young boy, they had to make sure that they're sexually active, that they are healthy people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they had to have, first, sex.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once they had it, they were sent to a writing desk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Under the writing desk was an x-ray machine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And with x-ray, how do-- 'waves,' they call it? 'Waves?' With x-ray waves was set up the waves that between the legs, to give me the-- the X should be burned out.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All these boys and girls, they didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They all died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is only one boy was still alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why was he alive?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because he had an uncle, a kapo, a foreman, a Jew, who, whenever was a selection and whenever they saw a struggling, sick boy-- between those boys and girls, he was hiding him aside.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he was hidden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still saw one of him-- this boy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was crying day and night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why my uncle doesn't let me to die?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm suffering.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It hurts.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's-- that's the type experiments they made.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- they made shades from human-- from human skin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They still-- you can get, even today-- it's a big prize.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can get a piece of soap what it says, 'Reines Judisches Fett.' I will show you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have a-- I'm sorry that I bring it to you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I will send this picture I have to send you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They made a special grave in Hungary in a certain town that all the soaps what were still left over are buried.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's details-- where it was done, what date it was done, and where was it done.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Soap from human beings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Always.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Always.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But only Jews.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The selection was always done-- twice was it done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, two occasion it was done-- the selection.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
